generated_description: dl plast, legally known as dlplast s.r.o., is a company based in holešov, zlín, specializing in the extrusion of plastic hoses and profiles, plastic product injection, and plastic waste processing. the company produces a variety of hoses, including steel spiral, polyurethane with pvc spiral reinforcement, and spiral-reinforced flexible hoses made from pvc polymers. dl plast has a production capacity of 20 extrusion presses and has marketed over 1000 tons of plastic hoses annually, making it one of the top eu manufacturers. the company has also installed a new production line for window sills and a double profile line for spiral hoses. dl plast is certified by tüv cert and adheres to iso quality management standards.
